00:19:51.720 --> 00:19:52.640 line:20%
'Sai!'

00:19:53.040 --> 00:19:54.160 line:20%
'Hai!'

00:19:54.200 --> 00:19:56.760 line:20%
'Hai!  Apa yang sedang kamu lakukan?'

00:19:57.360 --> 00:20:00.120 line:20%
'Aku akan segera
